{"tid":866263,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲垃圾港男成日要去外國丟假？","createTime":"2018-10-17T17:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T08:01:11.000Z","uid":178365,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9d31a6770f3447a267b2ef2171283448dc4771","tid":866263,"uid":178365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T17:14:50.000Z","msg":"今日搭台北機場捷運<br />\n有個男人係咁鬧個女朋友唔上車<br />\n實情係佢女朋友讓個抱住小朋友嘅阿嬸落車先至唔上住<br />\n我話佢條女有禮貌<br />\n之後條粉皮就爆曬粗咁撩交打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n丟晒香港人假<br />\n條女早日搵過個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c499b12b5cedef9dd8a66f2e2b72a5c379631298","tid":866263,"uid":140538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:24:32.000Z","msg":"好多港男去到日本勁講粗口， 以為好撚威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5153450d6aafb8d9dedeaeacea8d5272401ed1dc","tid":866263,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T14:30:07.000Z","msg":"根本香港人同支那人一樣<br />\n只係作地係香港怕比人影上網先唔會咁放肆<br />\n但係一去到外地就原形畢露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班都冇家教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f10f2dc18aed41f079bd59fed197671ad889b3","tid":866263,"uid":178365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:57:31.000Z","msg":"其實唔止港男<br />\n啲港女都係咁<br />\n有一次去排隊買嘢食<br />\n人哋畫好咗圍欄<br />\n圍欄入面就係出菜<br />\n啲職員拎住啲嘢食嘢飲走嚟走去<br />\n食客就個個都係排圍欄外面<br />\n點知有個港女死都要行入去圍欄入面<br />\n人哋叫佢出返外面佢仲要寸柒柒大大聲咁用國語講「我知道」<br />\n但係又唔出返去<br />\n真係見到都覺得丟架"},{"pid":"4b6ac05b41c01c01984c987f47527b84ebfaf6a0","tid":866263,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:01:11.000Z","msg":"去過旅行就知 一家大細個啲先麻撚煩 態度又差到爆"}]}